WEBVTT

00:01.030 --> 00:02.372
- WHY CAN'T I JUST STAY HERE?

00:02.480 --> 00:04.539
- WE'RE ALL GONNA LIVE TOGETHER
AS A BIG HAPPY FAMILY.

00:04.650 --> 00:06.891
- I DON'T WANT TO GO.

00:07.000 --> 00:08.103
- KRISTINA, UNFORTUNATELY,

00:08.210 --> 00:09.302
ONE OF THE NODES
THAT WE REMOVED HAS CANCER.

00:09.420 --> 00:11.342
- I'M SORRY--TREATMENT.
- WILL IT GO AWAY?

00:11.450 --> 00:13.657
- DO YOU SAY THAT'S
SHE'S GONNA NEED CHEMOTHERAPY?

00:15.220 --> 00:16.380
- HEY. YOU REMEMBER ME?

00:16.490 --> 00:18.071
- MY GRANDPA'S FRIEND.
- RIGHT.

00:18.190 --> 00:19.566
WOULD YOU GO OUT
WITH ME SOMETIME?

00:19.670 --> 00:20.329
- YEAH.

00:20.430 --> 00:22.421
- I MET A GUY THIS SUMMER.

00:22.530 --> 00:24.873
- WHAT, ARE YOU, LIKE, BREAKING
UP WITH ME OR SOMETHING?

00:24.990 --> 00:27.015
- I STILL WANT TO BE FRIENDS.

00:27.130 --> 00:28.392
- [scoffs]

00:29.680 --> 00:31.841
- LOOK, FOR THE RECORD,

00:31.960 --> 00:33.097
I REALLY THINK THIS
IS AN AWFUL IDEA.

00:33.200 --> 00:35.236
- YES, I KNOW YOU THINK
THIS IS A BAD IDEA.

00:35.340 --> 00:36.375
- I'M SERIOUS.
IT'S TERRIBLE.

00:36.480 --> 00:37.139
I MEAN, WHAT ARE YOU
EVEN THINKING?

00:37.240 --> 00:40.038
- YOU KNOW, SHE'S SICK.

00:40.140 --> 00:43.348
IT'S JUST A NICE,
LIKE, GET-WELL BASKET.

00:43.450 --> 00:44.929
- YOU'RE HER EX-BOYFRIEND.
- I KNOW.

00:45.040 --> 00:46.348
- WHY ARE YOU GIVING HER--
- BUT I'M TRYING

00:46.460 --> 00:48.007
NOT TO BE HER EX-BOYFRIEND.
THAT'S THE WHOLE POINT.

00:48.110 --> 00:49.384
- THIS IS NOT THE WAY TO DO IT.

00:49.490 --> 00:52.971
SHE'S GONNA THINK THAT
IT'S CREEPY AND--AND SAD.

00:53.080 --> 00:54.695
I MEAN, WHAT IS THIS STUFF EVEN?
- THIS IS HER HOUSE. THAT ONE.

00:54.810 --> 00:56.869
I DON'T WANT TO TALK ABOUT IT.
- LIKE TEA, AND LIKE,

00:56.980 --> 00:58.390
A FILTERING WATER BO'I'I'LE?

00:58.500 --> 01:00.252
WHERE DID YOU EVEN GET THIS?
- I GOT IT FROM AUNT KRISTINA.

01:00.370 --> 01:03.157
SHE GOT A BUNCH OF BASKETS
AND TOLD ME I COULD TAKE IT.

01:03.270 --> 01:05.056
- WAIT A SECOND, I'M SORRY.

01:05.160 --> 01:06.502
YOU'RE RE-GIFI'ING
A CANCER PATIENT'S...

01:06.610 --> 01:08.919
- YES, I KNOW IT SOUNDS BAD,
BUT SHE TOLD ME TO TAKE IT.

01:09.030 --> 01:10.190
- GIFI' BASKET
TO YOUR EX-GIRLFRIEND

01:10.310 --> 01:12.471
