TO COME OVER.

01:12.580 --> 01:15.378
- OH, MY GOSH.
- PLEASE DON'T DO IT.

01:15.480 --> 01:18.825
WE CAN HAVE LUNCH.
- JUST WAIT HERE FOR ME.

01:27.910 --> 01:30.458
[dog barking]

01:35.400 --> 01:36.742
UM--

01:36.850 --> 01:38.078
